question: What fast food restaurant is available on the path leading to Bottle & Bottega, North Olmsted, OH from Barons Bus Arena, Parma, OH, within a radius of 150 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.758046 41.416012)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.898988 41.419561)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.758046 41.416012)',4326)::geography, 150000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.758046 41.416012)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.poi_name: Hot Dog Tony's Restaurant and Bar
